(Tuesday June 9 2015), 11394=Win Tickets To N5L With Vital Football (Friday June 5 2015), 12405=Pemberton Tips City To Do Well Next Term (Monday June 22 2015), 18044=Time: 1:59PM, 12614=No Offers For Freeman Or Any Other Players (Monday June 29 2015), 12821=Goalkeeper Speculation Starts With Bunn (Monday June 29 2015), 20496=Bristol City have been placed in the South-West area section ahead of the draw for the first round of this season's Johnstone's Paint Trophy. City missed out on being drawn for a bye into the next round and go into the hat for the draw which will as usual; take place on Soccer AM on 17th August. The Robins will be drawn against one of the following clubs: Bristol Rovers, Cheltenham Town, Exeter City, Plymouth Argyle, Portsmouth, Torquay United or Wycombe Wanderers., 13022=Agard To Start Season On Sideline (Thursday July 2 2015), 12004=Burton Albion Show An Interest In JET (Friday June 12 2015), 13224=The Supporters Summit - Bristol City (Friday July 3 2015)}
